---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — Syed Gibran"
  description="You don't need a reason. Just say hi."
  canonical="https://syedgibran.com/contact/"
>

  <main id="main-content">

    <section class="contact-header">
      <div class="container">

        <p class="label">you made it here</p>

        <h1 class="contact-header__title">
          You don't need<br />a reason.
        </h1>

        <div class="contact-header__body">
          <p>
            You opened this page. That already means something.
            Most people read and leave. You stayed long enough
            to wonder if there was a way to reach the person
            behind the words.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before you talk yourself out of it — and you are
            already talking yourself out of it — I want you
            to know something.
          </p>
          <p>
            You don't need a question worth asking or an insight
            worth sharing or a problem important enough to justify
            the message. You don't need to have read everything
            or figured out something profound or have anything
            to offer in return.
          </p>
          <p>You can just say hi.</p>
          <p>
            Tell me about your week. Tell me where you are in
            the rebuild. Tell me what is crumbling right now or
            what just started to hold. Tell me you are still
            showing up even though nothing has moved yet.
          </p>
          <p>That is enough. That is more than enough.</p>
          <p>
            I read everything. It is just me on the other side
            of this.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
      <svg class="crack" viewBox="0 0 720 20" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0 10 L120 10 L145 4 L170 14 L192 7 L220 11 L258 5 L290 12 L320 8 L360 10 L720 10"
          fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75"
          stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <section class="contact-form-section">
      <div class="container">

        <form
          class="contact-form"
          action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit"
          method="POST"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="fd1ad569-8d5f-449d-9cea-37a1b6706835" />
          <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="https://syedgibran.com/thankyou/" />
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="New message from syedgibran.com" />

          <div class="contact-form__field">
            <label for="name" class="contact-form__label">your name</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              class="contact-form__input"
              placeholder="what do people call you"
              required
              autocomplete="name"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="contact-form__field">
            <label for="email" class="contact-form__label">your email</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              class="contact-form__input"
              placeholder="so I can write back"
              required
              autocomplete="email"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="contact-form__field">
            <label for="message" class="contact-form__label">your message</label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              class="contact-form__textarea"
              placeholder="say anything. hi is enough."
              rows="6"
              required
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="contact-form__submit">
            send it
          </button>

        </form>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

</Layout>